Game Description
******************

Play Griddlers. Ted and P.E.T. and enjoy a brand-new puzzle adventure! In this Griddlers game, you travel back in time with scientist Ted and P.E.T., his robot friend. Use the new and improved controls to solve more than 100 mind-boggling puzzles. Complete extra tasks, earn more than 15 trophies, and enjoy the wonderful soundtrack. Train your brain with Griddlers. Ted and P.E.T. now!

Game Features
***************

*travel back in time in a new Griddlers puzzle challenge
*visit 6 different locations to solve more than 100 unique puzzles
*choose your training level and follow a skill-specific tutorial
*earn trophies for completing 3 levels in a row without using hints, solving puzzles in less than 30 seconds, and more

